      <data key="d2">Reported diagnostic performance metric of the breath sensor when classifying Alzheimer’s disease versus healthy controls, achieving 85% accuracy in the NCT01291550 study. | Reported diagnostic performance metric of the breath sensor when classifying Alzheimer’s disease versus Parkinson’s disease, achieving only 15% accuracy in the NCT01291550 study, indicating poor discrimination between these two disease states.</data>
