      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A plasmonic nanoparticle-based biosensor platform that enables naked-eye detection of SARS-CoV-2 by using antisense oligonucleotides targeting the viral N gene to induce a colorimetric change, functioning as a nucleic acid detection assay (non-CRISPR).</data>
