      <data key="d1">REPORTER_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d2">An electrochemical readout (current or potential change) generated at gold nanoparticle-modified carbon electrodes upon binding of MERS-CoV antigens, serving as the measurable output of the immunosensor. | The electrochemical readout generated by the paper-based immunosensor upon binding of avian influenza virus antigens, serving as the measurable reporter signal of the assay.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.8</data>
