      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">An in vivo nanosensor platform described by Harvey et al. (2019, Nano Lett.) that measures compartment-specific exposure to the chemotherapeutic drug doxorubicin within living organisms.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.86</data>
