      <data key="d1">REPORTER_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d2">The measured readout corresponding to local concentration or exposure levels of the chemotherapeutic agent doxorubicin in different in vivo compartments, as reported by the nanosensor.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.7</data>
      <data key="d4">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_526</data>
