      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A nanometallic conductive composite-hydrogel core–shell microneedle skin patch developed by Zhang et al. (2023, Nanoscale) for real-time monitoring of interstitial analytes through minimally invasive skin insertion.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_526</data>
