      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A high-sensitivity biosensor platform combining a porous silk fibroin substrate with gold nanocracks to create a surface-enhanced Raman scattering (SERS) interface, as reported by Choi et al. (2021, Biosensors).</data>
