      <data key="d2">Reported limit of detection for Dengue DNA hybridization using Mn2O3 nanofiber-based electrochemical sensing electrodes, given as 120 × 10^-21 M (equivalent to 1.20 × 10^-19 M).</data>
      <data key="d3">0.85</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_17</data>
