      <data key="d0">LOD RANGING FROM 40 TO 3,000 COPIES</data>
      <data key="d1">LIMIT_OF_DETECTION</data>
      <data key="d2">The reported limit of detection range for different influenza A virus subtypes in the integrated microfluidic system developed by Shen et al.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_24</data>
      <data key="d5">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1</data>
    </node>
    <node id="PORTABLE CENTRIFUGAL MICROFLUIDIC SYSTEM">
      <data key="d0">PORTABLE CENTRIFUGAL MICROFLUIDIC SYSTEM</data>
      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A CD-shaped centrifugal microfluidic platform that integrates multi-step nucleic acid testing on-chip using spinning-induced centrifugal forces and passive valves to automate solution mixing, nucleic acid extraction, amplification, and detection.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_25</data>
