      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A portable, pop-up diagnostic laboratory approximately twice the size of a standard cupboard moving box, deployable in low-resource settings with a total capacity of about 14,000 COVID-19 tests and on-site reagent synthesis based on synthetic biology.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.96</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_28</data>
