      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A paper-based synthetic biology diagnostic platform where commercially available cell-free expression systems are freeze-dried onto cellulose filter paper, enabling long-term (&gt;1 year) room-temperature storage and abiotic distribution of gene circuit-based reagents.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.94</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_28</data>
