      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">Synthetic RNA sensor constructs known as toehold switches, used as a low-cost point-of-care diagnostic platform when combined with freeze-dried cell-free systems for detecting viral RNA such as Zika virus.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_28</data>
