      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">An integrated disposable cartridge for the GeneXpert System that performs automated SARS-CoV-2 nucleic acid testing, including fluid transport via plunger rod-operated valve rotation and virus disruption by sonication. | A cartridge-based RT-PCR assay for SARS-CoV-2 that integrates sample preparation, amplification, and detection in a single-use lab-in-a-cartridge format with minimal hands-on time.</data>
      <data key="d3">1.0</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_29,ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_30</data>
