      <data key="d1">AMPLIFICATION_METHOD</data>
      <data key="d2">A real-time reverse-transcription PCR (RT-PCR) method that converts viral RNA to cDNA and amplifies it with real-time fluorescence monitoring, used here for detection of a novel human coronavirus.</data>
