      <data key="d0">CRISPR-C2C2</data>
      <data key="d1">CAS_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d2">An earlier designation for the Cas13a family of RNA-guided RNases; exhibits two distinct RNase activities that enable both guide-RNA processing and collateral RNA cleavage for detection.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.8</data>
      <data key="d4">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_50,ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_52</data>
