      <data key="d2">An Abbott m2000 RealTime SARS-CoV-2 EUA test run on a sealed 96-well optical reaction plate, representing a lab-in-a-plate high-throughput nucleic acid amplification platform for COVID-19 RNA detection. | A lab-based real-time RT-PCR diagnostic assay for SARS-CoV-2 run on the m2000™RealTime System using a sealed Abbott 96-well optical reaction plate, supporting high-throughput automated processing of respiratory samples.</data>
