      <data key="d1">AMPLIFICATION_METHOD</data>
      <data key="d2">A nucleic acid amplification method that simultaneously amplifies multiple target sequences in a single reaction, used in the BioFire COVID-19 Test to detect several SARS-CoV-2 genomic regions. | A multiplex reverse transcription PCR method used in the Panther Fusion® SARS-CoV-2 Assay to simultaneously amplify multiple viral targets, including SARS-CoV-2 and other respiratory viruses.</data>
