      <data key="d0">PAGE BAND PATTERNS</data>
      <data key="d1">REPORTER_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d2">Polyacrylamide gel electrophoresis (PAGE) band patterns, including intact R structure bands and fading R bands, used to visualize cleavage and product formation in ANCA reactions.</data>
