    <node id="R REPORTER STRAND">
      <data key="d0">R REPORTER STRAND</data>
      <data key="d1">REPORTER_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d2">A fluorophore- and quencher-labeled DNA reporter sequence (R) whose cleavage and degradation generate a fluorescence signal in the ANCA method; optimal performance is achieved when labels are attached only to R. | A complementary or auxiliary reporter sequence (R*) used together with R in the ANCA method; dual labeling of both R and R* with fluorophore and quencher reduces reaction efficiency, likely due to steric hindrance.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_15</data>
      <data key="d5">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b</data>
