      <data key="d2">Blinded diagnostic test run using rectal swab samples that were initially negative and then randomly spiked with KPC-producing K. pneumoniae to supplement clinical specimens for ANCA performance evaluation. | Diagnostic test run using transport media from negatively diagnosed rectal swabs that were randomly spiked with IMP-producing K. pneumoniae to generate IMP-positive specimens for IMP circuit evaluation.</data>
