      <data key="d1">ASSAY_VALIDATION</data>
      <data key="d2">Validation study of the ANCA method using 200 total clinical and KPC-spiked rectal swab samples, reporting 100% clinical sensitivity, 98.7% specificity, and ROC AUC of 0.9997 compared to PCR.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.96</data>
      <data key="d4">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_27</data>
