      <data key="d1">ASSAY_VALIDATION</data>
      <data key="d2">Validation study of the IMP circuit using 160 clinical and mock clinical specimens (80 IMP-positive, 80 negative), reporting 100% clinical sensitivity, 100% specificity, and ROC AUC of 1.0.</data>
