      <data key="d0">RECTAL SWAB-IMMERSED TRANSPORT MEDIA SAMPLE</data>
      <data key="d1">ASSAY_RUN</data>
      <data key="d2">Assay condition in which the rectal swab is first immersed in 5 mL of transport media and the media is then used in the ANCA method, resulting in diluted bacterial concentration and lower sensitivity.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.84</data>
      <data key="d4">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_29</data>
      <data key="d5">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b</data>
    </node>
