      <data key="d0">ARGONAUTE INTEGRATED SINGLE-TUBE PCR SYSTEM</data>
      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A single-tube assay that integrates Argonaute protein activity with PCR to enable supersensitive detection of rare mutations, as described by Liu et al. in Nucleic Acids Research (2021).</data>
      <data key="d3">0.85</data>
      <data key="d4">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_56</data>
      <data key="d5">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b</data>
