      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A paper-based integrated one-step assay that combines thermal lysis and loop-mediated isothermal DNA amplification (LAMP) to detect DNA from E. coli and M. smegmatis cells within 30 minutes.</data>
