      <data key="d0">SYNTHETIC BIOSENSORS</data>
      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">Engineered biosensing systems, ranging from individual biomolecules to whole-cell constructs, designed for low-cost, rapid diagnostics, continuous monitoring, dosimetry, and remote sensing outside the laboratory.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_27</data>
