      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">Biosensing platforms that use living cells as the sensing element, capable of sustained surveillance and rapid response to external signals. | Biosensing platforms that operate without living cells, historically focused on nucleic acid detection but recently expanded via metabolic transducer modules.</data>
