      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">Biosensing platforms based on living cells, offering a wide range of currently developed detection capabilities for outside-the-lab applications. | Engineered living cells used as biosensors that can be deployed in the field for continuous hazard detection, including fluorescence or luminescence-based readouts.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.86</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_44</data>
