      <data key="d0">ONE-POT SENSING REACTIONS</data>
      <data key="d1">SAMPLE_PREP_STEP</data>
      <data key="d2">Sample preparation approach where unprocessed samples are directly added to a single reaction mixture that combines all necessary processing and sensing steps, reducing user intervention.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.78</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_49</data>
      <data key="d5">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="MICROFLUIDICS-BASED INTERFACES">
      <data key="d0">MICROFLUIDICS-BASED INTERFACES</data>
      <data key="d1">SAMPLE_PREP_STEP</data>
      <data key="d2">Integrated microfluidic sample processing modules that automate handling, conditioning, and delivery of complex samples to biosensing reactions without extensive user input.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.7</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_49</data>
      <data key="d5">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="PAPER-BASED INTERFACES">
      <data key="d0">PAPER-BASED INTERFACES</data>
      <data key="d1">SAMPLE_PREP_STEP</data>
      <data key="d2">Paper-based sample processing and delivery formats that perform filtration, reagent storage, and fluidic control to prepare samples for biosensing in low-resource settings.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.7</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_49</data>
      <data key="d5">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="USER-FRIENDLY INTERFACING FOR BIOSENSING PLATFORMS">
      <data key="d0">USER-FRIENDLY INTERFACING FOR BIOSENSING PLATFORMS</data>
      <data key="d1">SAMPLE_PREP_STEP</data>
      <data key="d2">General strategy of integrating one-pot reactions, microfluidics, and paper-based formats to simplify sample input and processing for biosensing platforms, especially in low-resource environments.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.65</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_49</data>
      <data key="d5">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="ENGINEERING OF SENSING CIRCUITS FOR COMPLEX MIXTURES">
      <data key="d0">ENGINEERING OF SENSING CIRCUITS FOR COMPLEX MIXTURES</data>
      <data key="d1">SAMPLE_PREP_STEP</data>
      <data key="d2">Design and modification of biosensing reaction components and logic to tolerate or process complex, unprocessed sample matrices without extensive upstream purification.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.6</data>
      <data key="d4">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_49</data>
      <data key="d5">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </node>
