      <data key="d1">BIOSENSOR_PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d2">A biosensor platform implemented in the sediment bacterium Shewanella oneidensis, engineered to produce gas reporter signals for monitoring gene expression and environmental hazards in soils.</data>
