      <data key="d10">DETECTR is used to detect SARS-CoV-2 by targeting viral nucleic acids, enabling rapid identification of the virus compared with conventional methods. | DETECTR is mentioned as a CRISPR-based system used for viral detection during the SARS-CoV-2 pandemic, and its test kit is authorized for SARS-CoV-2 detection. | DETECTR has been implemented for SARS-CoV-2 detection using Cas12a-mediated cleavage of reporter molecules upon recognition of viral genomic targets.</data>
