      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">Optimized RT-qPCR assays retain detection capability at viral concentrations below 10³ copies mL⁻¹ in water and aerosols, indicating suitability for early infection detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
