      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">In the PfAgo-based assay, cDNA produced by RT-PCR is subjected to Argonaute cleavage, ultimately yielding a fluorescent signal as the readout of SARS-CoV-2 detection.</data>
