      <data key="d8">RT-PCR</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The statement that SHERLOCK’s sensitivity is comparable to RT-PCR is defined relative to RT-PCR, which serves as the reference amplification method in the validation context.</data>
