      <data key="d8">NANOTECHNOLOGY–GENETIC DETECTION MICROPLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Naked-eye detection of viruses is achieved by using a nanotechnology–genetic detection microplatform that produces a visually interpretable signal, such as a color change, readable without instrumentation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_86</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR" target="SARS-COV-2">
      <data key="d7">N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The N-gene targeting plasmonic nanoparticle colorimetric sensor selectively detects SARS-CoV-2 by recognizing sequences in the viral N gene, enabling visual identification of the virus without complex instrumentation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_87</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR" target="N-GENE TARGETING ANTISENSE OLIGONUCLEOTIDE CAPPED PLASMONIC NANOPARTICLES">
      <data key="d7">N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">N-GENE TARGETING ANTISENSE OLIGONUCLEOTIDE CAPPED PLASMONIC NANOPARTICLES</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">The biosensor platform employs N-gene-targeting ASO-capped plasmonic nanoparticles as the signal-generating element; their interaction with SARS-CoV-2 N-gene sequences produces the optical change used for detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_87</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR" target="COLORIMETRIC READOUT (NAKED-EYE DETECTION)">
      <data key="d7">N-GENE TARGETING NPS COLORIMETRIC SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">COLORIMETRIC READOUT (NAKED-EYE DETECTION)</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">The platform reports detection events as a colorimetric change visible to the naked eye, which serves as the primary readout for the presence of SARS-CoV-2.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_87</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="ELECTROCHEMICAL IMMUNOSENSOR WITH AUNP-MODIFIED ARRAY ELECTRODES" target="MERS-COV">
      <data key="d7">ELECTROCHEMICAL IMMUNOSENSOR WITH AUNP-MODIFIED ARRAY ELECTRODES</data>
      <data key="d8">MERS-COV</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The electrochemical immunosensor employing a dielectric electrophoresis array of AuNP-modified carbon electrodes detects MERS-CoV by capturing viral antigens and transducing binding events into measurable electrochemical changes.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_87</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="ELECTROCHEMICAL IMMUNOSENSOR WITH AUNP-MODIFIED ARRAY ELECTRODES" target="ELECTROCHEMICAL SIGNAL (CURRENT, POTENTIAL, IMPEDANCE CHANGES)">
      <data key="d7">ELECTROCHEMICAL IMMUNOSENSOR WITH AUNP-MODIFIED ARRAY ELECTRODES</data>
      <data key="d8">ELECTROCHEMICAL SIGNAL (CURRENT, POTENTIAL, IMPEDANCE CHANGES)</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">When MERS-CoV is captured on the AuNP-modified electrodes, the immunosensor produces changes in current, potential, or impedance that constitute the electrochemical reporter signal for virus detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a_chunk_87</data>
      <data key="d14">f2b3cfad-751c-4e9d-a9ef-77be12b8fc1a</data>
    </edge>
