      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The antisense oligonucleotide sequences on the plasmonic nanoparticles are complementary to the SARS-CoV-2 N gene, enabling sequence-specific recognition and thus selective detection of the virus within the colorimetric platform.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
