      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">PCR is used as a molecular method to detect SARS-CoV-2 nucleic acids, serving as a confirmatory test following negative antigen assays and as a sensitivity benchmark.</data>
