      <data key="d8">FOODBORNE PATHOGENIC BACTERIA</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">In the Argonaute-triggered detection of foodborne pathogenic bacteria, PCR amplifies bacterial DNA that is then processed by Argonaute proteins for fluorescent readout.</data>
