      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">In the foodborne bacterial detection workflow, PCR-amplified DNA is processed by Argonaute proteins, generating a fluorescent signal through cleavage of a reporter probe.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.75</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_8</data>
