      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">CRISPR-based detection systems such as SHERLOCK, DETECTR, and STOPCovid are highlighted as emerging tools for viral detection in the context of the SARS-CoV-2 pandemic, implying their use for detecting SARS-CoV-2.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
