      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">During the early acute phase of SARS-CoV-2 infection, diagnosis should rely on molecular nucleic acid amplification using RT-PCR to detect viral RNA via cDNA generation and amplification.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
