      <data key="d8">QRT-PCR</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">In the early acute phase of SARS-CoV-2 infection, qRT-PCR is commonly used as a highly sensitive amplification method to detect viral RNA when antibodies are not yet detectable.</data>
