      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">RT-LAMP DETECTS pathogenic avian influenza by reverse transcribing and amplifying viral nucleic acids at a fixed temperature, enabling rapid and specific identification of avian influenza viruses in diagnostic assays.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
