      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">RT-LAMP DETECTS respiratory viruses by reverse transcribing and amplifying their nucleic acids in a one-step isothermal reaction, supporting rapid screening of multiple respiratory viral pathogens.</data>
