      <data key="d8">TRACE ASSAY</data>
      <data key="d9">OUTPERFORMS</data>
      <data key="d10">The lateral flow TRACE assay operationally outperforms more equipment-intensive TRACE formats for point-of-care use by fulfilling ASSURED criteria, although analytical sensitivity is not directly compared.</data>
