      <data key="d8">BIND-WASH-ELUTE PROTOCOL ON SILICA-COATED MAGNETIC BEADS</data>
      <data key="d9">REQUIRES_PREP</data>
      <data key="d10">The centrifugal microfluidic system incorporates a bind-wash-elute protocol on silica-coated magnetic beads as the nucleic acid extraction step required to purify viral RNA before amplification and detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_25</data>
      <data key="d14">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1</data>
    </edge>
