      <data key="d7">PORTABLE CENTRIFUGAL MICROFLUIDIC SYSTEM</data>
      <data key="d8">PREAMPLIFIED RNA ALIQUOTING INTO 13 CHAMBERS THROUGH CENTRIFUGATION</data>
      <data key="d9">REQUIRES_PREP</data>
      <data key="d10">The platform uses centrifugal forces to aliquot preamplified RNA into 13 reaction chambers, a required on-chip distribution step that enables multiplexed amplification and detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1_chunk_25</data>
      <data key="d14">ed45ef2f-ad29-4058-8b09-5fed00b411a1</data>
    </edge>
