      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The lab-in-a-cartridge system reported by Xu et al. detects influenza virus by integrating RNA extraction with multi-chamber RT-PCR, enabling rapid influenza diagnostics within 2.5 hours.</data>
