      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">Functional studies demonstrate that TRACE can simultaneously detect pathogen DNA and host gene targets as internal controls at comparable sensitivity, overcoming a key limitation of many CRISPR assays.</data>
