      <data key="d8">CRISPR-CAS12A</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">The Cas12aVDet platform employs CRISPR-Cas12a as its core detection nuclease, using Cas12a’s target-activated nonspecific ssDNase activity to convert target recognition into a visual signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.98</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
