      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The Cas12aVDet platform integrates a nucleic acid amplification step with Cas12a-based detection in a single tube, pre-amplifying target sequences to enhance sensitivity while streamlining the workflow.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_4</data>
