    <edge source="CONTAMINATION-FREE VISUAL DETECTION OF SARS-COV-2 WITH CRISPR/CAS12A" target="SARS-COV-2">
      <data key="d7">CONTAMINATION-FREE VISUAL DETECTION OF SARS-COV-2 WITH CRISPR/CAS12A</data>
      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">This CRISPR-Cas12a-based assay is specifically configured to detect SARS-CoV-2 nucleic acids, providing a visual readout suitable for point-of-care testing. | The contamination-free visual CRISPR/Cas12a assay is configured to detect SARS-CoV-2 as its target pathogen in point-of-care settings.</data>
