      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">Suboptimal- or no-PAM gRNAs are used within one-pot CRISPR–NAA assays to reduce Cas12a activity during ongoing amplification, helping preserve amplicon levels and balance amplification with detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
