      <data key="d8">NAA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">One-pot CRISPR–NAA assays incorporate a nucleic acid amplification (NAA) reaction whose amplicons are simultaneously used as targets for CRISPR detection within the same reaction mixture.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
