      <data key="d8">RPA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE one-pot duplex assay platform leverages the temperature profile of RPA to perform nucleic acid amplification as part of its thermally orchestrated detection workflow.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.96</data>
