      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE thermally segregates a general nucleic acid amplification (NAA) phase from CRISPR activity, using amplification to boost low-abundance targets before CRISPR-based readout.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
