      <data key="d7">TRACE ASSAY</data>
      <data key="d8">PROBE DEGRADATION</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Upon target recognition by the Cas12b:gRNA complex in the high-temperature stage, TRACE induces probe degradation, which serves as the primary biochemical reporter signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
