      <data key="d8">LATERAL FLOW ASSAY STRIPS</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE can output results as a visual signal on lateral flow assay strips, where probe cleavage products are translated into bands that indicate positive or negative detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
