      <data key="d8">PORTABLE DEVICE</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE can be interfaced with a portable device that reads the reporter signal generated by probe degradation, enabling electronic visualization of assay results at the point of care.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
