      <data key="d8">MONKEYPOX VIRUS (MPXV)</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay is designed to detect monkeypox virus by targeting a conserved region of the MPXV J2L gene for point-of-care diagnosis.</data>
