      <data key="d8">RECOMBINASE-AIDED AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay is compatible with recombinase-aided amplification, another RPA-like method, broadening the range of amplification chemistries that can feed into the CRISPR detection step.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_14</data>
