      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay demonstrates a functional limit of detection of 0.5 focus-forming units per milliliter of MPXV viral particles under the optimized reaction conditions.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.93</data>
