      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay exhibits a broad linear detection range from 10 to 10,000 target copies per test, defining its quantitative dynamic range for MPXV DNA detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
