      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">At or above 5 copies per test, the TRACE assay reliably detects MPXV DNA in at least 95% of synthetic replicate samples, representing a practical sensitivity benchmark.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.87</data>
