      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">The reported limits of detection and performance metrics for the TRACE assay are associated with a 40-minute two-temperature run protocol (10 min at 37 °C and 30 min at 60 °C).</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_14</data>
      <data key="d14">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d</data>
