      <data key="d8">TRACE WORKFLOW TIME (25 MIN SAMPLE-TO-RESULT)</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE provides a sample-to-result workflow of about 25 minutes, supporting its classification as a rapid point-of-care test.</data>
