      <data key="d8">ASSURED CRITERIA</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE is reported to meet the ASSURED criteria for optimal point-of-care testing: Affordable, Sensitive, Specific, User-friendly, Rapid, Equipment-free, and Delivered.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
