      <data key="d8">AAPCAS12B</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay is a CRISPR-based detection platform that relies on Cas effector enzymes, and AapCas12b binding properties are evaluated in the surrounding context, indicating that AapCas12b is a candidate or component nuclease used by TRACE for target recognition and cleavage.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
