      <data key="d8">RPA PELLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">RPA pellets represent the physical formulation of the RPA amplification method that is co-developed and co-stored with TRACE, indicating that the TRACE assay uses these pellets as its amplification module.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
