      <data key="d8">LYOPHILIZED CRISPR PELLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">REQUIRES_PREP</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE master mixes are processed via freezing at -50 °C and vacuum drying at -40 °C to generate lyophilized CRISPR pellets, which serve as the prepared assay format for storage and later use, making lyophilization a required preparation step for the platform’s deployable form.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_43</data>
