      <data key="d8">LONG-TERM STABILITY ASSESSMENT</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The long-term stability assessment, in which lyophilized CRISPR pellets are stored at 37 °C and tested over 0–60 days, serves as a validation study for the TRACE assay’s stability and performance over time.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_43</data>
