      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">During the subsequent 30 minutes, the TRACE assay produces a stage-2 fluorescence change (ΔF2) that reflects detection of the MPXV J2L gene target.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
