      <data key="d10">The TRACE assay generates real-time fluorescence signals recorded every minute by either the SLAN-96 system or a portable reader, enabling kinetic monitoring of both RNase P and J2L targets. | The TRACE assay generates fluorescence signals that are measured to obtain MPXV detection results.</data>
