      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The choice of the 18-min TRACE protocol is justified because its diagnostic performance (95% correct identification of samples, 95% CI 89–98) fulfills the external guideline for MPXV nucleic acid detection, validating this specific assay run configuration.</data>
