      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The TRACE lateral flow assay is designed as a point-of-care platform to detect MPXV in clinical specimens for on-site screening in resource-limited settings. | The TRACE lateral flow assay is designed as a point-of-care test that detects MPXV in clinical specimens by targeting viral DNA.</data>
