      <data key="d10">The duplex TRACE assay uses recombinase polymerase amplification (RPA) in stage-1 to amplify nucleic acid targets before Cas12a detection; both stage-1 and stage-2 are run for 30 minutes to mitigate competition between RPA and Cas12a and improve RNase P detection.</data>
