      <data key="d9">OUTPERFORMS</data>
      <data key="d10">CRISPR-based assays are proposed to complement and, in decentralized settings, outperform qPCR in terms of speed and portability for on-site detection of HPAI, despite qPCR remaining the laboratory gold standard.</data>
