      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">CRISPR-based assays are cited as rapid diagnostic methods intended to detect viral pathogens such as avian influenza virus, complementing slower virus isolation for outbreak response.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.6</data>
