      <data key="d8">CAS VARIANTS</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">The SHERLOCK V2 system is a multiplexed CRISPR detection framework that relies on distinct Cas variants, serving as a conceptual model for future TRACE designs that would require new Cas variants with distinct temperature and trans-cleavage profiles.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_35</data>
