      <data key="d8">MPXV</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">TRACE assays are used to detect MPXV in lysates of diverse patient specimen types, supporting rapid diagnosis of this human pathogen.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
