      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">AapCas12b is incubated with 5′-FAM-labeled gRNA to form RNP complexes, demonstrating that this Cas variant uses the guide RNA as its targeting component for nucleic acid recognition.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_43</data>
