      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">AapCas12b is incubated with an annealed gRNA–ssRNA blocker mixture, where the gRNA component still serves as the targeting guide but is partially sequestered by the ssRNA blocker, allowing evaluation of how blocked guide RNA affects RNP formation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
