      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">The outpatient validation study demonstrates that TRACE LFA results are fully concordant with qPCR on nucleic acid extracts, indicating high specificity relative to the reference method.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
