      <data key="d8">GRNA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The CRISPR detection step uses designed gRNA sequences to confer specificity toward MPXV genomic targets during the assay.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
