    </edge>
    <edge source="CRISPR DETECTION STEP" target="IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE">
      <data key="d7">CRISPR DETECTION STEP</data>
      <data key="d8">IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">CRISPR gRNAs are aligned to the in-silico database to evaluate mismatch tolerance and specificity, confirming that they target MPXV while avoiding non-target genomes.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_38</data>
      <data key="d14">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE" target="PATHOGEN NUCLEIC ACID PANEL FOR SPECIFICITY ASSESSMENT">
      <data key="d7">IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE</data>
      <data key="d8">PATHOGEN NUCLEIC ACID PANEL FOR SPECIFICITY ASSESSMENT</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">The composition of the in-silico database parallels the diversity of pathogen nucleic acids used in wet-lab specificity testing, together defining the assay’s specificity profile against MPXV and non-target pathogens.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_38</data>
      <data key="d14">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE" target="MPXV">
      <data key="d7">IN-SILICO MPXV AND NON-MPXV REFERENCE DATABASE</data>
      <data key="d8">MPXV</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_SPECIFICITY</data>
      <data key="d10">By including 2,525 complete MPXV genomes, the in-silico database enables evaluation of how robustly primers and gRNAs cover MPXV genetic diversity while maintaining specificity.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_38</data>
      <data key="d14">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d</data>
    </edge>
