      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The ACE system incorporates 5′-BHQ1-ssRNA blocker 1 to hybridize with gRNA 1, forming a quenched complex that controls the timing and extent of Cas12b activation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_41</data>
