      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">The ACE system produces fluorescence signals from FAM-labeled gRNA 1 and its quenched complex with the BHQ1-labeled ssRNA blocker, which are recorded over time and temperature to assess blocker-mediated control.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
