      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The one-pot assays employ gRNA 1 to direct Cas12b to its target sequence, with gRNA availability influenced by its interaction with the ssRNA blocker and reaction temperature.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6f94756d-fd42-4a77-b6b1-d9dc6901591d_chunk_41</data>
