      <data key="d8">SSRNA BLOCKER 1</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The one-pot assays include ssRNA blocker 1 to transiently suppress gRNA 1 activity, enabling controlled activation of Cas12b during the course of the reaction.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.75</data>
