      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">FAM-labeled gRNA 1 generates fluorescence signals that are modulated by hybridization with the BHQ1-labeled ssRNA blocker and by temperature-dependent dissociation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
