      <data key="d8">SSRNA BLOCKER 1</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">gRNA 1 hybridizes with ssRNA blocker 1 in a 1:4 ratio to form a quenched complex whose dissociation dynamics are studied across a range of temperatures.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
