      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The dCas12b variant is combined with gRNA in a 1:1 ratio to form RNP complexes for dsDNA binding assays, indicating that dCas12b also uses the same guide RNA for sequence-specific binding.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
