      <data key="d8">RT-QPCR</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The Targeted Biosensing &amp; Diagnostics track incorporates RT-qPCR as a core amplification-based assay for high-specificity confirmation of suspected avian influenza infections.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
