      <data key="d8">CRISPR-BASED ASSAYS</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">Within the Targeted Biosensing &amp; Diagnostics track, CRISPR-based assays serve as frontier molecular diagnostics that can validate and characterize avian influenza infections following initial screening.</data>
