      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The Targeted Biosensing &amp; Diagnostics track includes CRISPR-Cas–based methods as high-specificity molecular diagnostics that confirm and refine detection of avian influenza virus.</data>
