      <data key="d8">RT-RPA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The platform uses RT-RPA as a pre-amplification step to increase viral nucleic-acid copies, enhancing the sensitivity of subsequent Cas12a-based detection.</data>
