      <data key="d8">6.7 COPIES/ΜL LIMIT OF DETECTION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_LOD</data>
      <data key="d10">The platform achieves a limit of detection of 6.7 copies per microliter, indicating high analytical sensitivity for H5 avian influenza virus targets.</data>
