      <data key="d8">RT-RPA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">These systems employ RT-RPA as one of the isothermal amplification methods to convert and amplify RNA targets prior to Cas12a-based detection.</data>
