      <data key="d8">WET CYCLONE SAMPLER</data>
      <data key="d9">REQUIRES_PREP</data>
      <data key="d10">For airborne measurements, the biosensor is applied to liquid samples obtained by pre-collecting aerosols with a wet cyclone sampler.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_51</data>
