      <data key="d8">SERIAL DILUTIONS IN PBS</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The sensitivity and linearity of the capacitive biosensor for H5N1 detection are validated using serial dilutions of H5N1 in PBS, yielding a strong linear correlation between normalized ΔC% and log concentration.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_51</data>
