      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Binding of target pathogens to the capture probes on the capacitive biosensor produces a measurable normalized ΔC% change in capacitance that serves as the reporter signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_51</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
