    <edge source="CAPACITIVE BIOSENSOR FOR RAPID DETECTION OF AVIAN (H5N1) INFLUENZA AND E. COLI IN AEROSOLS" target="AVIAN INFLUENZA A H5N1 VIRUS">
      <data key="d7">CAPACITIVE BIOSENSOR FOR RAPID DETECTION OF AVIAN (H5N1) INFLUENZA AND E. COLI IN AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d8">AVIAN INFLUENZA A (H5N1) VIRUS</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The capacitive biosensor platform is designed to detect avian influenza A (H5N1) virus present in aerosols by monitoring changes in capacitance upon binding of the viral particles.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.98</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_79</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
