      <data key="d8">ESCHERICHIA COLI (E. COLI)</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The capacitive biosensor platform is also configured to detect aerosolized Escherichia coli, using capacitance changes as a signal for the presence of this bacterial target in air samples.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
