      <data key="d9">OUTPERFORMS</data>
      <data key="d10">Within a multimodal avian influenza virus workflow, the chip is positioned as a high-sensitivity confirmatory channel rather than a frontline on-farm screen, complementing but not replacing other modalities.</data>
