      <data key="d8">INFLUENZA A</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The clean-matrix SERS workflow detects and distinguishes Influenza A from other viruses using spectral and PCA-LDA features.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_58</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="SERS-BASED VIRAL DETECTION WORKFLOW IN CLEAN CELL SUPERNATANT" target="ZIKA VIRUS">
      <data key="d7">SERS-BASED VIRAL DETECTION WORKFLOW IN CLEAN CELL SUPERNATANT</data>
      <data key="d8">ZIKA VIRUS</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The SERS workflow in clean cell supernatant identifies Zika virus as a distinct class based on its SERS spectral signature and PCA-LDA separation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_58</data>
