    <edge source="PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR" target="AVIAN INFLUENZA">
      <data key="d7">PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">AVIAN INFLUENZA</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The portable SERS-based aerosol sensor is proposed as an early warning system in poultry farms by detecting spectral fingerprints associated with avian influenza or its infection-related metabolites in airborne aerosols from chicken houses.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_59</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR" target="TRADITIONAL QPCR">
      <data key="d7">PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">TRADITIONAL QPCR</data>
      <data key="d9">OUTPERFORMS</data>
      <data key="d10">For initial, broad surveillance, the portable SERS-based aerosol sensor provides non-targeted, minutes-scale detection directly from air with minimal sample processing, offering faster and broader preliminary screening than traditional qPCR, which is reserved for targeted confirmatory identification.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_59</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR" target="ANTIGEN ASSAYS">
      <data key="d7">PORTABLE SERS-BASED AEROSOL SENSOR</data>
      <data key="d8">ANTIGEN ASSAYS</data>
      <data key="d9">OUTPERFORMS</data>
      <data key="d10">As a non-targeted, rapid screening tool, the portable SERS-based aerosol sensor can flag unexpected or novel pathogens via their chemical fingerprints earlier and across a broader range than antigen assays, which are subsequently used for specific confirmation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.75</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_59</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="MACHINE-LEARNING-ENABLED SERS PLATFORM" target="FIVE RESPIRATORY VIRUSES">
      <data key="d7">MACHINE-LEARNING-ENABLED SERS PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d8">FIVE RESPIRATORY VIRUSES</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The machine-learning-enabled SERS platform learns SERS spectral differences in complex biological media to rapidly detect and classify five different respiratory viruses from aerosol samples in a single measurement.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_59</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="CRISPR-CAS PLATFORMS" target="SINGLE-GUIDE RNA">
      <data key="d7">CRISPR-CHIP PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d8">SINGLE-GUIDE RNA</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_GUIDE</data>
      <data key="d10">The CRISPR-chip platform employs single-guide RNA to direct immobilized dCas9 to specific target nucleic acid sequences, enabling sequence-specific electrical detection.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_47</data>
      <data key="d14">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="CRISPR-CAS PLATFORMS" target="AMPLIFICATION">
      <data key="d7">CRISPR-CHIP PLATFORM</data>
      <data key="d8">AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_AMPLIFICATION</data>
      <data key="d10">The CRISPR-chip platform is designed to bypass the need for nucleic acid amplification, functioning without the amplification step that many other CRISPR assays require.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_47</data>
      <data key="d14">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </edge>
