      <data key="d8">ON-SITE CRISPR ASSAY</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The approximately 1-hour turnaround characterizes the run conditions of the on-site CRISPR assay, specifying that a single assay run delivers a diagnostic result within about one hour from sampling.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_66</data>
