      <data key="d8">ELECTROCHEMICAL IMPEDANCE ASSAYS</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Within Tier 2, electrochemical impedance assays function as a biosensor platform that produces impedance-based signals used to rapidly infer the presence of HPAI-related targets.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.78</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b_chunk_68</data>
      <data key="d14">de3c3a3b-6855-4b40-bff9-eef9df2e0d4b</data>
    </edge>
