      <data key="d10">The PAM-independent CRISPR-Cas12a assay, combined with RPA and anti-NP antibody-based viral RNA purification, is explicitly described as enabling rapid and specific on-site diagnosis of H5Nx avian influenza, indicating that this platform is designed to detect H5Nx avian influenza viruses.</data>
