      <data key="d8">RESPIRATORY VIRUSES</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The SERS-based biosensor platform described by Yang et al. (2022) detects and quantifies respiratory viruses by measuring enhanced Raman spectra and applying machine learning for viral identification.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
