      <data key="d8">INFLUENZA VIRUSES</data>
      <data key="d9">DETECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The reduced graphene oxide-based electrochemical immunosensor integrated with a microfluidic platform is configured to detect influenza viruses by capturing viral particles or antigens on antibody-functionalized graphene electrodes and transducing binding events into an electrochemical signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.96</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
