      <data key="d7">CRISPR/CAS12 SYSTEM</data>
      <data key="d8">CAS12</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">The CRISPR/Cas12 diagnostic system is built around the Cas12 nuclease as its effector enzyme, which mediates both target recognition and collateral cleavage of single-stranded DNA.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.99</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_4</data>
