      <data key="d8">DNA REPORTER FOR CRISPR/CAS12A</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Cas12-based diagnostic platforms, including those using Cas12a, employ cleavable DNA reporters whose degradation by Cas12 collateral activity produces the diagnostic signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.85</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_4</data>
