      <data key="d7">HOLMESV2</data>
      <data key="d8">CAS12</data>
      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">HOLMESv2 is described as a CRISPR-Cas12b-assisted platform, indicating that it uses a Cas12-family nuclease (Cas12b) as its core detection enzyme.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
