      <data key="d7">HOLMESV2</data>
      <data key="d8">COLLATERAL CLEAVAGE ACTIVITY OF CAS12</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">HOLMESv2 leverages Cas12b’s collateral cleavage of single-stranded DNA as an amplified reporter signal, enabling sensitive nucleic acid detection and DNA methylation quantitation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">8cd80207-0825-48ce-af82-eed721eee13b_chunk_4</data>
