      <data key="d8">COLORIMETRIC READOUT</data>
      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Upon target recognition by CRISPR/dCas9, the assay generates a colorimetric readout as the reporter signal.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.98</data>
