      <data key="d9">USES_VARIANT</data>
      <data key="d10">The HOLMESv2 platform employs Cas12b as its core CRISPR effector nuclease for nucleic acid detection and DNA methylation quantitation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
