      <data key="d8">STORE-BOUGHT HAND WARMER AS THE INCUBATOR</data>
      <data key="d9">REQUIRES_PREP</data>
      <data key="d10">The dual CRISPR-Cas12a assay uses a store-bought hand warmer as an improvised incubator to maintain reaction temperature, enabling field deployment without laboratory equipment.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f_chunk_42</data>
      <data key="d14">4b595dc6-a258-44ed-89fc-c349fc64a77f</data>
    </edge>
