      <data key="d9">PRODUCES_SIGNAL</data>
      <data key="d10">Upon successful detection of SARS-CoV-2, the dual CRISPR-Cas12a assay generates a signal that can be read visually by eye under LED illumination, providing an instrument-free readout.</data>
